  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Never Be Alone Again</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Too many phases around you,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Life makes you tired and weary.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>You seek for a path with your name on the side,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Reaching a way concerned but full of pride,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Sometimes you lead as you make it,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>When life reveals its ride.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>So run stay clever, to the place where you'll be found,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>We'll scream together, and try to push away the loss of time,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="9" type="stanza">
          <l>You will never be alone again.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="10" type="stanza">
          <l>Too many meanings you claim to find,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="11" type="stanza">
          <l>Defining but fading the same time.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="12" type="stanza">
          <l>Emancipation won't knock on your door,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="13" type="stanza">
          <l>Afraid of the moment when you'll return to this world,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="14" type="stanza">
          <l>But nowhere ashore.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="15" type="stanza">
          <l>So run...</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="16" type="stanza">
          <l>You seek for a path with your name on the side,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="17" type="stanza">
          <l>Reaching a way concerned but full of pride,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="18" type="stanza">
          <l>If you ain't there for yourself,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="19" type="stanza">
          <l>Who else will be? who else will see?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="20" type="stanza">
          <l>So run..</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
